            , JUN. I am a lace-merchant; my partners are 
               <persName id="t18220911-134-person1281">
                  James 
                  Fisher
               <interp inst="t18220911-134-person1281" type="surname" value="Fisher"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-134-person1281" type="given" value="James"></interp>
